ENAITURUK

Ore embuku e dukuya e SAMUEL neutu enkibelekenyata te Israel eiteru too larishak o meshomo erishata e nkitoria. Ore ena kibelekenyata to losho le Israel neutuno too ltung'ana o kuni laa: Samuel laa ninye olarishani obayie, Saul laa ninye olaiguanani le dukuya le Israel, o Daudi laa ore enkishui enye e dukuya eton eitu eaku olaiguanani nelimuno too mbaa naaipirare Samuel o Saul.

Ore embae kitok tena buku anaa kulie bukui oo nkatinin naasira to Sotua Musana, naa nchere ore enkisiligata e Nkai, neyau enkisulata, ore engolon enkong'u neyau enkidaata. Etolimuoki ena aaibalie too rorei lo Laitoriani eirorie olapolosani Eli tiatua 
2  .
30   ewueji nejo “Ekayanyit lelo laayanyit Nanu, ore lelo laamenaa Nanu naitame te ngoro napi.”

Ore ena buku netisira indamunot naapaashipaasha te nkitamanyunoto enkitoria. Ore Olaitoriani makewan naa ninye apa olaiguanani osipa le Israel, kake ore eng'amaroto natang'amua ninye eomonunoto oo ltung'ana, etegelaka Olaitoriani ninche olaiguanani. Ore embae e tipat naa ena: Ore olaiguanani tenebo iltung'ana le Israel netii apa abori enkitoria e Nkai (
2  .
7  -
10  ) Ore tiabori inkitanapat Enkai, ore esipata oo ltung'ana pooki aa ilkarsisi tenebo ilaisinak neramatieki pooki.

